<br>
Don't get me wrong.  I'm sure this will be a marginally useful spell line for the small segment of the wizard population that does raids in areas with gating mobs.  But as has been stated in many threads, it has nothing to do with the real issues, and pretty much shows that Verant has no intention of ever really trying to fix the class.<br>
<br>
And so, I leave.  I'm off to AO where the power-nuking class is actually viable, and brings some very nice tools to a group.<br>
<br>
/bye to my fellow wizards.<br>
